Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流动的水没有形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的风找不到踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.47,0:00:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取决于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天找出出人意料的凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的动机 意外的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.71,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似是小孩 头脑却异于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.60,0:01:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假里 我们因为旅行而去了长野的有森旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 我们碰到了企业家城元英彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演员备前千鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.78,0:01:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟兰 有森先生还有阿忍三个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.52,0:02:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到高原去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而城元先生跟宫部先生去钓鱼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于担心一整天都没见到的千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去她房间找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤小姐不是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被谋杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.31,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑天使的翅膀（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.69,0:02:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的星星真是太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都出神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.33,0:02:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美奈穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我们马上回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.81,0:03:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤小姐死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巴士留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们立刻回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是演员备前千鹤 30岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.19,0:03:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和丈夫城元英彦住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推定时间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推定时间是下午一点半到两点半之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是窒息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现尸体时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个保险扣是拴上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把门撞开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全部的窗户都是反锁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是备前千鹤是个有名的演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事令她自杀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 昨晚有突发事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突发事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她签约的电影公司的负责人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说赞助商要求换人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子 你不能进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个淘气鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你东张西望的干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里好像有些奇怪的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有什么奇怪的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里确实有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.17,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是有人想把这里变成一个密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这是怎么回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有人在里面把窗户上了锁以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了制造一间密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把保险扣从墙上取了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到走廊 把保险扣扣上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从外面把保险扣装好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.06,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是从外面拧螺丝太难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就留下了这样的擦痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把保险扣除下容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要装上去就困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.84,0:05:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤小姐就是用这个作垫子的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 哎哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍别人的调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 人的脚趾应该是有指纹的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.89,0:05:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问这么多干嘛 别多管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说千鹤小姐是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问这个台子上有没有千鹤小姐的脚趾指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人把千鹤小姐吊起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说是他杀而不是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚千鹤小姐去餐厅见谁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟上去看清楚就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么线索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是些白色的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这里也太热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.43,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道发现尸体的时候已经停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凶手特意关掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于备前千鹤小姐死的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一些问题要问你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 城元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像跟千鹤小姐正在办离婚手续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在只剩下了赡养费的问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是宫部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你要跟千鹤小姐解约是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这可不是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为赞助商要换人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我要问问大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤小姐死亡的时间大约是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午一点半到两点半之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家告诉我 你们那时候在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.69,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思 好像在调查不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道千鹤小姐是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现场情况来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他杀的可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说宫部先生和城元先生钓鱼去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上十点从旅馆出发 下午四点回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在湖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那个 我忘了带便当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二点回来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅馆的大厅里跟毛利先生一起吃了饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点半又离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.49,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你有没有看到千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来之后就马上去看她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我敲门却没有反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就又回大厅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城元先生回来时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫部先生不就是一个人了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一直在那里吃午饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生跟阿忍小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.92,0:08:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和小兰还有柯南去高原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元先生他们走后不久我们也出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达高原的时间大约是十一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就一直待在高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约六点我们才下山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到旅馆的时间大约是七点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有森先生一个人留在山上了 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为巴士的引擎坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去接他了 对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时他在高原吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.38,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去了 绝对没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈穗小姐和穗奈美小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上我们刚要打扫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看见城元先生回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟毛利先生一起吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们送茶时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去过大厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点半左右我们送走了城元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.21,0:09:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四点之前 我们就和毛利先生一起看电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家准备晚饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到大家回来 一直在厨房里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫时 千鹤小姐的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她不让我们打扫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们并没有接近那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 你一直在旅馆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一直在大厅里看电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了十二点半城元先生说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去看看而上过楼之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直没见过任何人上楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说凶手是从紧急出口上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出口的情况怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出口在走廊的尽头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从里面可以随意出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在外面没有钥匙就进不来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么凶手就是旅馆里的人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因为钥匙在我这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很清楚了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够这样做的人只有她们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们什么也没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点半到四点之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们一直都在和我看电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凶手就是你们三个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.48,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反  反正没有钥匙的我不是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见得 即使没有钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有办法从紧急出口进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见得 即使没有钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有办法从紧急出口进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如城元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二点半你去看千鹤小姐时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能从里面打开紧急出口的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.77,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后放上一些障碍物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让门不能关上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在一点半以去湖边为借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从紧急出口回到旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害了千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有这种可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫部先生 你也可能成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元先生的帮凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能跟城元先生一起回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又藏了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再利用城元先生打开的紧急出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入旅馆杀了千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你简直把他们当成犯人了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个又怎样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钥匙的只有你们两个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们下山不就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要乱说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从高原或湖边回到旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要经过森林里的一座桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才已经问过森林里的工人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回旅馆的只有城元先生的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有犯罪可能的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元 宫部 美奈穗 穗奈美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和毛利先生你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 我也是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水户警官说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定另有隐情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如关掉的空调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在千鹤小姐身上的白色粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是一条飞翔的跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.09,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护栏弄花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔让你去检查一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元 宫部 美奈穗 穗奈美 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我你们一整天的具体活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沉睡的小五郎推理秀的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这就是传闻中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事情就包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你已经知道凶手是谁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.14,0:13:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道凶手是谁以及凶手所用的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手是用翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把不可能变成可能的魔法的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.43,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森光行先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小兰他们一直都在高原上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.21,0:14:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有森先生不可能是凶手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有魔法的翅膀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的翅膀到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是魔法的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在储物室里发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是滑翔翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.51,0:14:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我发现在被害者的颈部有在屋顶阳台擦过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生利用滑翔翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从高原飞回旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后从屋顶上面爬到千鹤小姐的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再利用滑翔翼返回高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开大家去拿便当只有四 五分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来回这里至少要十五分钟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从旅馆再飞回山上的高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不太可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 大家说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.43,0:15:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要杀害千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要四 五分钟就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是待在千鹤小姐身边的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤她一直留在旅馆里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 还有巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.28,0:15:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出发时有森先生跟阿忍说他去锁门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另开一辆车和大家会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就到千鹤的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用高压电枪什么的把她弄昏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把她和滑翔翼都装上巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水户警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场勘查的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到那个空调没开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤小姐白天不在房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后大约两点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.71,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生在为大家拿便当时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.61,0:16:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴士内将千鹤小姐勒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后以巴士引擎坏了为由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人留在了高原上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后他打开滑翔翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上千鹤小姐的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从山上飞回了旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于旅馆屋顶的灯全亮着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就可以确定目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你降落在屋顶上以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就爬下阳台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.98,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从窗户进入屋内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把尸体吊了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.88,0:17:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再用我刚才说的方法关上门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从紧急出口离开了旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我又是怎样回到高原的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小兰到达高原的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的确在那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他是开巴士吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会被森林里的工人看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.64,0:17:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用滑翔翼飞回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很难再用它飞回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.08,0:17:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说他用魔法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了任何人都不知道的魔法回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的道具是你的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生打手机叫阿忍小姐去接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就藏在车子的后备箱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.53,0:17:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿忍小姐和兰不知不觉间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和有森先生一起回到了高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子到达高原时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到阿忍小姐和兰离开车子后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就钻出后备箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.01,0:18:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像一直在那里等着一样 出现在你们两人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你的推测而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.27,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才他们来电话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在千鹤小姐裙子上的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山上稀有蝴蝶的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你们所听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直留在旅馆的千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子上又怎么会有山上蝴蝶的粉末呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.69,0:18:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听兰说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高原时 有只蝴蝶曾飞到你的肩膀上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知什么原因死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就把粉末留在你身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你背千鹤小姐的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉末就沾到裙子上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把千鹤小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为弟弟报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.95,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟辉彦在东京读大学时碰到了千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉彦对美丽的千鹤越来越迷恋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对千鹤来说 她只是玩玩而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.83,0:19:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一开始她把弟弟当成有钱人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她交往 用了很多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤被名导演发掘后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越出名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于跟辉彦分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉彦为了挽回千鹤的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了不少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.95,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至把爸爸的遗产 也就是这家旅馆给抵押了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在这家旅馆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.23,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这家旅馆已经是别人的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的经营者另有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你弟弟怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉彦他自暴自弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.84,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后和滑翔翼一起坠落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟追逐千鹤小姐 就跟追逐太阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却因为太热而折断了翅膀的天使一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 千鹤她知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我昨晚叫她到餐厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.73,0:20:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想让她对弟弟道歉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对那照片一点印象也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.34,0:20:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你前男友有森辉彦的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟在跟你分手之后就自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自杀关我什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他自己喜欢上我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不是要责备你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.13,0:21:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望你在他坟前道个歉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自作主张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不会做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟我一点关系都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就决定要杀她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你弟弟会高兴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶的死虽然是偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却认为是你弟弟的灵魂为了阻止你犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.29,0:21:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作蝴蝶而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也太慢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底到哪里去了 真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.14,0:23:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.55,0:23:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是天使吗 怎么说也不像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被卡车撞倒的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.16,0:23:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地对逃跑的犯人叫着谜一样的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.93,0:23:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被命名为愁思郎事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时警察还展开了大规模的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.53,0:24:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因为掌握核心事件的警官已经过世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查就停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.84,0:24:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前已经过了追诉时效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.61,0:24:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.11,0:24:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本厅刑事恋爱物语3（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.42,0:24:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.92,0:24:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站指示牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.92,0:24:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集的舞台是警视厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.29,0:24:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官和佐藤警官怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.59,0:24:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.70,0:00:21.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,35)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}正因为你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.81,0:00:30.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}喜好不同 脚程与表达的方式也大异其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.31,0:00:37.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}如今我们在两人的记忆中正在渐渐褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.25,0:00:44.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(60,0)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我摸索过 却开始探寻其他人与未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.11,0:00:52.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我比自己想象的活得更坚强 追寻一种特别的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.27,0:00:56.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}为难以应付的每一天所苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.31,0:00:59.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx129}ture heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.53,0:01:06.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}为了不再迷惑 请别松开你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(30,40)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}即使是互相伤害的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.91,0:01:21.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我只是一直在迷惘的时空中找寻答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.53,0:01:27.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,800)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}朝着下一个舞台  {\fscx132}you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.31,0:01:32.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,800)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}请抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.23,0:01:39.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,730)}{\fs20}{\fscx101}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.13,0:22:01.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用什么方式表达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.80,0:22:08.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能让你明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.54,0:22:17.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那次以后 不知多少个季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.49,0:22:23.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是笑着守候在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.13,0:22:41.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不敢告诉我的事情 还有一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.64,0:22:46.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret of my heart 并不是怀疑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.55,0:22:52.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何时 只要还有少许未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.72,0:22:57.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相一定会落入手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.73,0:23:04.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法再说什么 只有等到机会
